awsMarketplace:AgreementType.description: Filters access by the type of the agreement.

awsMarketplace:PartyType.description: Filters access by the party type of the agreement.

awsMarketplace:ProductId.description: Filters access to AWS Marketplace RedHat OpenShift products in the RedHat console, based on the ProductID of the product. Note: This condition key only applies to the RedHat console, and using it will not allow access to products in AWS Marketplace.

catalog:ChangeType.description: Filters access by the change type in the StartChangeSet request
